<varlistentry id="options.Geometry">
	<term>Geometry</term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Completely or partially specifies the pager window location and
		geometry,  in  standard  X11  notation.  In order to maintain an
		undistorted aspect ratio, you might want to leave out either the
		width or height dimension of the geometry specification.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
